OL,3,CBoy, 14, seriously injured after fall
OL,4,Con Welsh mountain
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy was seriously
OL,7,Finjured after falling 20 to 30 metres
OL,8,Fin (Snowdonia) on Sunday.
OL,10,FThe incident happened on the
OL,11,Fnotoriously treacherous Tryfan peak
OL,12,Fwhile the boy was on a scrambling walk
OL,13,Fwith his mother, leading to a six-hour-
OL,14,Flong search and rescue operation.
OL,16,FThe 14-year-old, who was conscious,
OL,17,Fwas airlifted to with his mother and
OL,18,Fbrother, who arrived following the
OL,19,Faccident.
