OL,3,CBoy, 14, seriously injured after fall
OL,4,Con Welsh mountain
OL,6,FHis condition is unknown, although he
OL,7,Fis believed to have suffered possible
OL,8,Ffractures and facial injuries, as well
OL,9,Fas cuts and bruises.
OL,11,FUnable to get phone reception, his
OL,12,Fmother had to make the difficult
OL,13,Fdecision to leave her son to try to
OL,14,Fget help.
OL,16,FShe was picked up by a member of the
OL,17,Fpublic on a nearby road, who then
OL,18,Fcalled Ogwen Valley Mountain Rescue
OL,19,FTeam.
