OL,11,FRescue team spokesman Chris Lloyd
OL,12,Fsaid: "She was in a lot of distress.
OL,14,F"She said she had been with her son on
OL,15,FTryfan. They had not gone very far
OL,16,Fwhen he took a tumbling fall for
OL,17,Ftwenty to thirty metres in a gully.
OL,18,F"He was seriously injured and she made
OL,19,Fwhat must have been a very difficult
OL,20,Fdecision to come down off the mountain
OL,21,Fto get help."
